channel.title: Organized Storage
channel.description: I downloaded the organized storage mod and i went into the game. I fell from a high place 10 minutes later and died. I respawned and my crate wasn't there and in the chat it said something about my items being in a special crate that i made or something. I don't remember making one of these or where my items have gone.
